Package ca.gedge.opgraph.extensions

Provides support for the extension mechanism provided by the OpGraph project.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CompositeNode An extension meant for any OpNode that contains a graph (e.g., macro nodes).
CustomProcessing An extension meant for any OpNode that requires custom initialization, operation, and termination when being stepped into by a CustomProcessing.CustomProcessor.
CustomProcessing.CustomProcessor Interface for custom processors.
Extendable An interface for any class which would like to provide extensions to their functionality, even if the class is defined as final.
Publishable An extension that allows a field of a node to be "published".
 

Class Summary
ExtendableSupport Support class for the Extendable interface.
Publishable.PublishedInput An input field of a child node that is published for input to this macro.
Publishable.PublishedOutput An output field of a child node that is published for output from this macro.
 

Package ca.gedge.opgraph.extensions Description

Provides support for the extension mechanism provided by the OpGraph project. This package also provides some core extensions.
